tracks.text: The consigliere produces a large knife.
The consigliere tires to hand Jimmy the knife through the army base's fence, but the weapon is too large.
The knife bounces off the barbed wire, then falls into the consigliere's chest. He collapses in a pool of blood, twitching. Jimmy looks around then walks away.
At the house, Cookie and the kids eat breakfast. Jimmy carries golf clubs. He talks into a club as if it were a microphone.
Cookie throws eggs at his face.
